th `generated_loc: 0`, `tested_library_loc: 0`, `metadata_entries: 0`, and `code_coverage_percent: 0.0`.\n\n1. Replace the weakened smoke test with a non-trivial `2.0.5`-compatible test that still exercises the attribute-handling path through a public API, rather than only `Java7Reflector.isJava7()`.\n2. Rerun the coordinate test flow and regenerate coverage/stats for `org.codehaus.plexus:plexus-io:2.0.5`.\n3. Verify that `2.0.5` produces real dynamic-access coverage and does not regress from the existing `2.0.2` baseline of `2/2` reflection calls."}}
